                    </svg>
                    <p slot="first" class="section-title">Powerbrow: Soft and Natural Finish</p>
                    <p slot="second" class="section-desc">Powderbrow is a machine shading technique that will give you a soft powdery everday makeup look.</p>
                    <p slot="third" class="section-price">$500+ | 135 min</p>
                </Text>
                <Text>
                    <svg slot="icon" width="28" height="29" viewBox="0 0 28 29" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <rect x="14.0068" y="0.82196" width="19.5672" height="19.5672" transform="rotate(44.8861 14.0068 0.82196)" fill="black"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p slot="first" class="section-title">Microblading: Precise, Hair-like strokes</p>
                    <p slot="second" class="section-desc">Technique that combines microblading hairstrokes with powderbrow shading to create a realistic look.</p>
                    <p slot="third" class="section-price">$550+ | 150 min</p>
                </Text>
                <Text>
                    <svg slot="icon" width="28" height="29" viewBox="0 0 28 29" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <rect x="14.0068" y="0.82196" width="19.5672" height="19.5672" transform="rotate(44.8861 14.0068 0.82196)" fill="black"/>
                    </svg>
                    <p slot="first" class="section-title">Brow Tinting: Enhance your Natural Color</p>
                    <p slot="second" class="section-desc">Semi-permanent technique that dyes brow hairs and stains the skin slightly for a fuller, more defined appearance.</p>
                    <p slot="third" class="section-price">$500 | 135 min</p>
                </Text>
            </div>
            
            <button class="animate w-[140px] h-[50px] rounded-full bg-white border-2 border-[#543A14] text-xl text-[#543A14] box-border flex-none">Learn More</button>
        </div>
        
    </section>

    <section id="three" class="w-screen h-fit md:h-auto bg-[#FFFBEB] flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-5 md:gap-0 relative text-center md:text-left py-16">
