                and <b>ombre brow</b>, and love what i do and take pride in perfecting 
                my craft. </p>
            <button class="animate w-[140px] h-[50px] rounded-full bg-black text-white border-2 text-xl">Learn More</button>
         </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="contact" class="w-screen h-[700px] md:h-[600px] flex justify-center items-center relative bg-transparent">
        
        <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 1440 797" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M-0.908203 4.67728C269.985 -15.2934 485.729 37.5883 694.704 105.275C736.888 118.939 780.751 134.124 826.209 149.861C1006.98 212.445 1213 283.766 1439.09 302.886V796.235H-0.908203V4.67728Z" fill="#D0A46C"/>
        </svg>

